\f0\b0\fs42 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 2/3 cup {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.rickbayless.com/recipe/view?recipeID=244"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 Slow-Cooked Garlic Mojo }}(stir before measuring)(recipe below)\uc0\u8232 1 pound medium shrimp, peeled and (if you wish) deveined\u8232 Salt\u8232 1 to 3 canned chipotle chiles en adobo, seeded and finely chopped\u8232 1 pound dried linguine\u8232 2 or 3 tablespoons coarsely chopped watercress, parsley or cilantro\u8232 3/4 cup grated Mexican queso anejo, Parmesan or Romano\
